## Success Criteria
- Accurate implementation of the provided content/branding copy.
- Consistent design system (colors, typography, spacing).
- Smooth animations that respect `prefers-reduced-motion`.
- WCAG 2.1 AA compliance, semantic HTML, structured data.
- Deployable build (SSG/SSR) with clear path for future Arabic support.

## Constraints & Policies
- No internal Burooj Air microsite; all CTAs open `https://buroojair.com` in a new tab.
