- Prefer Tailwind CSS utilities; keep code extensible for CMS/i18n future phases.
- Follow Memory Bank workflow for planning, execution, validation, documentation.

## Stakeholders & Audience
- Internal: Burooj leadership, marketing, engineering partners.
